Package it.cnr.isti.thematrix.configuration.mapping

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractMapping
    Class for a mapping descriptor of a IAD attribute, handles the AbstractMapping XML tag contents.
    ComplexMapping
    Class for a IAD dataset field mapped on a LIAD field with a complex mapping (where a lookup operation is needed), handles the ComplexMapping XML tag.
    Dataset
    Class for the mapping schema of a IAD dataset, handles the dataset XML tag.
    IadMapping
    This is the ROOT element of the XML configuration file for the mapping between the DBMS (LIAD) records and the IAD schema
    LookupMapping
    Class for a mapping descriptor of a lookup mapping, handles the lookupMapping XML tag.
    LookupOperation
    Class for a mapping descriptor of a lookup mapping, handles the lookupOperation XML tag.
    Mapping
    Class for a mapping descriptor, handles the mapping XML tag.
    MultiMapping
    Class for a mapping descriptor of a multiple mapping, handles the multiMapping XML tag.
    RecodingTable
    Class for a recoding table inside a a mapping descriptor, handles the recodingTable XML tag.
    SimpleMapping  
    Value
    Elementary class for an XML ground pair, named after the entries in a recoding table.
    VoidMapping
    Class for the a void mapping descriptor (cannot map any LIAD information to IAD, leave theIAD field empty) , handles the voidMapping XML tag.
